name: AI LinkedIn Lead Gen System with n8n, Apify, and DeepSeek V3.1 to Replace Clay

parameters.content: ## Step 1: Search for Target Company with Apify & Sales Navigator
## Step 2: Get Company Background & Website with Perplexity
## Step 3: Email Enrichment Waterfall with Prospeo & Skrapp
## Step 4: Send Customized Email with Email Agent

parameters.text:
=Generate a cold email body selling AndyNoCode to {{ $('Limit').item.json.first_name }} at {{ $('Limit').item.json.name }} using their company description: "{{ $('Format JSON').item.json.output.description }}". 

Follow this structure/pattern:
I came across [COMPANY NAME] and [UNIQUE ASPECT FROM DESCRIPTION] - [BENEFIT STATEMENT].  

Our no-code API helps [SPECIFIC PAIN POINT] by [CORE SOLUTION], [QUANTIFIED OUTCOME]. Perfect for [TARGET USER ROLE] needing [KEY CAPABILITY].  

Would [NATURAL TRANSITION] to [CLEAR NEXT STEP]? [LOW-PRESSURE REQUEST].

Example Output:
I came across ABC Limited and your unique approach to providing cost-effective executive talent - it's an impressive solution for businesses needing flexibility.  

I'm reaching out because Andynocode could help streamline your workflows even further. Our no-code API simplifies social media automation, saving time and reducing manual effort. It's perfect for teams that need to scale efficiency without added complexity.  

Would you be open to a quick chat to explore how Andynocode could support ABC Limited's growth? Let me know a time that works for you.

Requirements:
- Mirror example's conversational flow
- Reference specific company traits from description
- Include 2-3 natural mentions of "AndyNoCode"
- Keep 3 short paragraphs (4 sentences max each)
- Focus on operational impact over technical specs
- No greetings/closings/subject line
- Plain text only (no formatting)

parameters.subject: We have a new product announced!
